PrecisAuthority to issue an INSTRUMENT OF RATIFICATION of the United Nations Convention on Prohibitions or Restrictions on the use of certain CONVENTIONAL WEAPONS which may be deemed to be excessively injurious or to have indiscriminate effects, together with its three Protocols, namely: . 1.
